Interface EventHandler<E extends Event<?>>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EventListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AutomaticType, CollectorType, ConstraintType, CounterType, EventMulticaster, RelationAlias, RelationView, RelationWrapper
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface EventHandler<E extends Event<?>>
extends EventListener
    An extended event listener interface that requires from implementations to provide a single handleEvent(Event) method.
